nd of crazy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn an effort to build/expand community - I built Airport Swap.  It is a platform to exchange rides to/from the airport \u003cem\u003efor free\u003c/em\u003e.  Give a ride to get a ride!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAirport Swap is was built with the intention of building (or finding) community or relying on a circle of trust to choose drivers/riders (friends of friends pretty much).  Connecting people on their street, in their building, or from a board game group they attended before is the goal.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLooking for any feedback :)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCheers!\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"I've been living in Denver for a few years and the prices for simple airport rides are kind of crazy.\r\n\r\nIn an effort to build/expand community - I built Airport Swap.  It is a platform to exchange rides to/from the airport _for free_.  Give a ride to get a ride!\r\n\r\nAirport Swap is was built with the intention of building (or finding) community or relying on a circle of trust to choose drivers/riders (friends of friends pretty much).  Connecting people on their street, in their building, or from a board game group they attended before is the goal. \r\n\r\nLooking for any feedback :) \r\n\r\nCheers!","submitter_user":"kzisme","user_is_author":true,"tags":["show","web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/1br6fz","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/1br6fz/free_airport_ride_exchange_platform"},{"short_id":"p6ihyc","created_at":"2026-03-16T17:49:25.000-05:00","title":"Avian Physics 0.6","url":"https://joonaa.dev/blog/12/avian-0-6","score":17,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"ancienthero","user_is_author":false,"tags":["games","release","rust"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/p6ihyc","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/p6ihyc/avian_physics_0_6"},{"short_id":"sfvqfr","created_at":"2026-03-17T06:32:26.000-05:00","title":"Ways of Seeing the Web","url":